 Step-by-step Implementation Roadmap
✅ Step	Description
✅ main() & Server class OCF	
▶️ Server::run()	Setup listening socket, poll loop
👤 Client class	Track nickname, username, socket, registration status
📡 Command Parser	Handle IRC commands (PASS, NICK, USER, JOIN, etc.)
💬 Channel logic	Implement JOIN, PRIVMSG, TOPIC, KICK...
⚠️ Error handling	Invalid commands, wrong password, duplicate nicknames
🔒 Password protection	Require client to send correct PASS before continuing
🧪 Test with netcat, irssi, or weechat	Connect with real IRC clients
📃 Subject compliance check	Make sure all mandatory commands and behaviors are implemented
